title: [SOLVED]820-4924 - No video.
message: I restored 3V42 and the board is booting now but it's not putting out any video/backlight. Thunderbolt external video is fine. Boots normally to desktop. I'm using a known-good test screen. Flashlight through the back gives me nothing. I'm attaching pre-ultrasonic pics. It's pretty obvious where it got hit. Not sure where to go with this one.
